Inner Healing
==========================================================
Inner healing a special type of feeling that emerge from inside, it never related to thought, It cant be created by thought.
It is experience observe by meditator during their journey.Only you feel from inside, the pepole around are unknown 
about it since they dont coress these experience.
If you share to some one who don't such type of experience they take it as normal.

In this state your frequency of feeling match to romantic songs,work out,speaking,listening...etc and since due to matching of 
frequecy with many things your frequency heal and you feel dilight.
Whatever the things come infornt of your life they realize of a tremendous feeling.

After this experience normally the percepiton of life changes

